### Get all coffee mugs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coffeemugs

### Get coffee mug by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/coffeemugs/1

### Create coffee mug (with nested coffee)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/coffeemugs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "color": "blue",
    "capacityMl": 350,
    "clean": true,
    "coffee": {
        "id": 1,
        "origin": "Ethiopia",
        "brewMethod": "FILTER"
    }
}

### Create coffee mug (without coffee)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/coffeemugs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "color": "red",
    "capacityMl": 250,
    "clean": false,
    "coffee": null
}

### Update coffee mug
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/coffeemugs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "color": "green",
    "capacityMl": 400,
    "clean": true,
    "coffee": {
        "id": 1,
        "origin": "Ethiopia",
        "brewMethod": "FILTER"
    }
}

### Delete coffee mug
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/coffeemugs/1
